580
00:43:04,645 --> 00:43:07,125
If she finds out we don't sleep together,
she'll be suspicious.

581
00:43:07,605 --> 00:43:09,005
But we signed a contract.

582
00:43:09,365 --> 00:43:11,445
An Ran, she isn't my friend.

583
00:43:11,885 --> 00:43:12,965
She's my wife.

584
00:43:13,405 --> 00:43:15,405
I don't have an ulterior motive.

